/* 
Demo Kaya diagram

This demo is designed to demonstrate a few features of Kaya in a somewhat
realistic way without being overwhelming.
*/

# L1
## Stack
### main
x: ptr(H0)
y: ptr(H1)
## Heap
H0: 1
H1: (4, ptr(H2))
##
H2: (2, *)

# L2
## Stack
### main
x: ptr(H0)
y: *
z: ptr(H2).ds
## Heap
H0: 1
H1: (4, ptr(H2))
##
H2: (2, *)
